Author: WigglyMuffin, CryoTechnic
Description:
Originally created by Liza Carvelli, now maintained and improved by WigglyMuffin and CryoTechnic.

A tiny little quest helper plugin that automates quests where possible. Uses navmesh to automatically walk to all quest waypoints, and tries to automatically complete all steps along the way.

Not all quests are supported, check Discord for support.

Required Plugins: vnavmesh, TextAdvance, Lifestream
Name: Questionable
Punchline: The actively maintained and improved quest helper plugin.

Author: WigglyMuffin
Description:
Created by Liza Carvelli, maintained by WigglyMuffin.

Uploads your game statistics (such as quest progress, gil, retainer stats) to an InfluxDB or QuestDB instance, making it possible to automatically track your progress through external tools such as Grafana.
Name: Influx
Punchline: Sync game stats to InfluxDB or QuestDB

Author: MacaronDream
Description: Automatically switches between characters based on quest completions and executes predefined sequences via Questionable integration. Use /qstcomp to open the main window.
Name: Questionable Companion
Punchline: Automated character rotation and quest sequence execution
